import Myimg from "../../images/svg-2.svg";
import img2 from "../../images/svg-1.svg";
import img3 from "../../images/svg-3.svg";

export const homeObj = {
  id: "about",
  lightBg: true,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: "NEW SOLUTION",
  headline: "YOUR NEXT STEP AHEAD.",
  description:
    "We use social media to tell you things that you could not see before.",
  buttonLable: "GET STARTED",
  imgstart: false,
  img: Myimg,
  alt: "twitter",
  dark: false,
  primary: true,
  darkText: true,
};

export const homeObj2 = {
  id: "why",
  lightBg: false,
  lightText: true,
  lightTextDesc: true,
  topLine: "",
  headline: "YOUR NEXT STEP AHEAD.",
  description:
    "We use social media to tell you things that you could not see before.",
  buttonLable: "GET STARTED",
  imgstart: true,
  img: img2,
  alt: "twitter",
  dark: true,
  primary: false,
  darkText: false,
};

export const homeObj3 = {
  id: "how",
  lightBg: true,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: "NEW SOLUTION",
  headline: "YOUR NEXT STEP AHEAD.",
  description:
    "We use social media to tell you things that you could not see before.",
  buttonLable: "GET STARTED",
  imgstart: false,
  img: img3,
  alt: "twitter",
  dark: false,
  primary: true,
  darkText: true,
};
